snippet.title: Oniken Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Oniken on http://www.desura.com/games/oniken !

More about Oniken on http://oniken.net . Oniken is a JoyMasher game http://joymasher.com/

Trailer by Gabriel Camelo http://cargocollective.com/camelo
Music by N-Freq  contact@n-freq.com

Oniken Full Version Features:

-6 Missions divided in 3 stages each
-Boss Rush Mode
-11 Bosses
-10 Mini Bosses
-Awesome Cutscenes
-Online Leaderboards
